Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,访问确认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切换至GEJI姐模式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在这里的机器到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是EGI系统
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EGI？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定期向宇宙发送特定频率声音的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过口袋电脑就可以听见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说君岛孝打算在这个岛上做些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是机密事项
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君岛孝是怎么死的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人是被谋杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被…被谋杀的？被谁？
